{"tid":552291,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)永不退縮1-3 意外殺手","createTime":"2018-02-06T11:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T17:36:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"777a6bd3c893792fa8f2b3f9c51a0d72bd62cf4f","tid":552291,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=mu2LrHILOiGtTxQfSHgwNIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8092eb44\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=mu2LrHILOiGtTxQfSHgwNIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=16ada6dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/39/Never_back_down.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F3%2F39%2FNever_back_down.jpg&h=469b477b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e4/Never_Back_Down_2_dvd_cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fe%2Fe4%2FNever_Back_Down_2_dvd_cover.jpg&h=79e45b67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://mov.mm52.net/2016/never_back_down_3/never_back_down_3_0001_620px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmov.mm52.net%2F2016%2Fnever_back_down_3%2Fnever_back_down_3_0001_620px.jpg&h=de958c58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://rental.asia1.com.tw/uploads/product/PD1516802295438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frental.asia1.com.tw%2Fuploads%2Fproduct%2FPD1516802295438.jpg&h=27488fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.傑克（肖恩&middot;法瑞斯 飾演）跟隨著家人一起移居到佛羅里達州的奧蘭多市，因為只有在這裡，才能給他的弟弟提供一個更好的職業網球的環境。在家鄉的時候，傑克是橄欖隊的明星球員，可是到了新的地方，他卻成了一個被人忽視的局外人，還落下了一個脾氣很臭、喜歡打架的壞名聲。傑克完全具備武術家的堅韌，雖然大多時候他都喜歡用拳頭來表達自己的想法，其實他是一個非常善良的人<br />\n<br />\n2.四個來自不同背景的拳擊手，卻找到彼此之間相同的嗜好。他們一起接受一位宗師的訓練，把目標放在拳擊賽場上的對決。未料，他們的宗師遭到惡劣的警察陷害，為了報一箭之仇，四個人將全力出擊...<br />\n<br />\n3.《永不退縮3》延續前作，講述了拳王凱西&middot;沃克再次征戰拳壇的故事。<br />\n<br />\n4.麥克&middot;福隆（斯科特&middot;阿金斯飾），號稱意外殺手的他，是位冷血殺手。就他從事的職業來講，他是頂尖的，無論是條理多樣的刺殺技巧，還是瞞天過海躲過警察視線，他的每次任務都使雇主滿意高興。但是有一天他摯愛的人卻捲入了倫敦的地下殺手世界，並慘遭自己同組織的人殺害。而福隆不得不打破自己長久以來井然有序，條理安排的生活，開始向實施這一切的人展開復仇<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=mu2LrHILOiGtTxQfSHgwNIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6543a648\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=mu2LrHILOiGtTxQfSHgwNIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d37adcf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a086397b0c8ce04223e9e0c6622087905b540ef","tid":552291,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{